config SPI_NUMAKER
	bool "Nuvoton NUMAKER MCU SPI driver"
	depends on SOC_FAMILY_NUMAKER
    select HAS_NUMAKER_SPI
    default y
	help
	  This option enables the SPI driver for Nuvoton NUMAKER family of processors. Say y if you wish to enable NUMAKER SPI.

